War Scream (X) 1
Emit a terrorizing roar that deals damage, pull nearby enemies, and add damage resistance to yourself and allies

Earth Mastery (R) 1
Increase you base damage from all Earth attacks

Thunder Mastery (R) 1
Increase you base damage from all Thunder attacks

Air Mastery (Y) 1
Increase you base damage from all Air attacks

Fire Mastery (B) 1
Increase you base damage from all Fire attacks

Water Mastery (Y) 1
Increase you base damage from all Water attacks

Quadruple Bash (R) 2
Bash will hit 4 times at an even farther range

Fireworks (R) 2
Mobs hit by Uppercut will explode mid-air and receive additional damage

Flyby Jab (X) 2
Damage enemies in your way when using Charge

Flaming Uppercut (B) 2
Uppercut will light mobs on fire dealing damage every 0.6 seconds

Half-Moon Swipe (Y) 2 (Y1)
Uppercut will deal a footsweep attack at a longer and wider angle. All elemental conversions become Water.

Generalist (Y) 2 (Y3)
After casting 3 different spells in row, your next spell will cost 5 Mana

Counter (Y) 2
When dodging a nearby enemy attack, get 30% change to instantly attack back

Mantle of the Bovemists (B) 2 (B3)
When casting War Scream, create a holy shield around you that reduces all incoming damage by 70% for 3 hits. (20s Cooldown)

Bak'al's Grasp (R) 2 (R2)
After casting War Scream, become Corrupted. (15s Cooldown)
You cannot heal while in that state.
while Corrupted, every 2% of health you lose will add +4 Raw Damage to your attacks. (Max 120)

